---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Premium Residential Campus | Lord Krishna Educational Academy">
    
    <section class="relative pt-12 pb-24 md:pt-16 md:pb-40 bg-blue-950 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-[0.03]" style="background-image: radial-gradient(#ffffff 1.5px, transparent 1.5px); background-size: 32px 32px;"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -translate-y-1/4 translate-x-1/4 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-amber-500/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none z-0"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 translate-y-1/4 -translate-x-1/4 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-blue-600/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none z-0"></div>

        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10 text-center">
            
            <div class="absolute -top-6 left-4 md:top-0 md:left-4 z-20">
                <a href="/" class="group flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 md:px-5 md:py-2.5 rounded-xl border border-slate-500/40 bg-blue-950/40 backdrop-blur-md text-slate-200 text-xs md:text-sm font-bold hover:text-amber-400 hover:border-amber-400/60 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(245,158,11,0.2)]">
                    <span class="group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform text-lg leading-none mb-0.5">←</span> Back to Home
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 border border-amber-500/40 bg-blue-900/50 backdrop-blur-md px-6 py-2 rounded-full mb-6 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(245,158,11,0.15)] hover:bg-blue-900/70 transition-colors cursor-default">
                <span class="text-amber-400 text-sm animate-pulse">✦</span>
                <span class="text-amber-400 text-[10px] md:text-xs font-black tracking-[0.25em] uppercase">LKEA Residential Campus</span>
                <span class="text-amber-400 text-sm animate-pulse">✦</span>
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-heading font-black text-white leading-[1.1] mb-6 tracking-tighter drop-shadow-2xl">
                A Disciplined Home for <br class="hidden md:block" />
                <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-200 via-amber-400 to-amber-500">Holistic Excellence</span>
            </h1>
            
            <p class="text-slate-200 text-sm md:text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-medium mb-10 drop-shadow-lg">
                We don't just provide a room; we provide an ecosystem. From morning yoga to meticulously supervised evening study sessions, our residential program is engineered to build unshakeable discipline, peak academic performance, and moral integrity in a completely secure, home-like environment.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 justify-center">
                <a href="/admission" class="bg-amber-500 text-blue-950 px-10 py-4.5 rounded-xl font-black text-lg shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(245,158,11,0.3)] hover:bg-amber-400 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                    <span>📝</span> Apply for Hostel Admission
                </a>
                <a href="#details" class="bg-blue-900/50 text-white border border-blue-400/30 backdrop-blur-md px-10 py-4.5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-blue-800 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 group">
                    Explore Facilities <span class="group-hover:translate-y-1 transition-transform">↓</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="relative z-20 -mt-10 md:-mt-14 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] border border-slate-100 p-2 md:p-4">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 divide-y md:divide-y-0 md:divide-x divide-slate-100">
                
                <div class="p-6 md:p-8 text-center hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors rounded-2xl">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🛡️</div>
                    <h4 class="font-black text-blue-950 text-xl mb-1">24×7</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">CCTV Security</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="p-6 md:p-8 text-center hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors rounded-2xl">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-3">👨‍🏫</div>
                    <h4 class="font-black text-blue-950 text-xl mb-1">Daily</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Supervised Study</p>
                </div>

                <div class="p-6 md:p-8 text-center hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors rounded-2xl">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🍲</div>
                    <h4 class="font-black text-blue-950 text-xl mb-1">A+ Grade</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Hygienic Food</p>
                </div>

                <div class="p-6 md:p-8 text-center hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors rounded-2xl">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-3">⚕️</div>
                    <h4 class="font-black text-blue-950 text-xl mb-1">24x7</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Medical Support</p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="relative z-3 -mt-8 md:-mt-12 py-12 md:py-20 bg-blue-950 rounded-t-[2.5rem] md:rounded-t-[4rem] shadow-[0_-15px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] border-t border-blue-800 border-b border-blue-900">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
            
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-1 block">The LKEA Edge</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-black text-white mb-4">A Highly Disciplined Routine</h2>
                <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-amber-500 mx-auto rounded-full mb-4"></div>
                <p class="text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
                    Success is born from daily habits. Our hostel routine is scientifically structured to balance mental sharpness, physical health, and rigorous academic focus.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4 group">
                    <div class="md:w-28 shrink-0 text-left md:text-right pt-2">
                        <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-white block leading-none">05:30 AM</span>
                        <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wide">Morning</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden md:flex flex-col items-center">
                        <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-amber-500 rounded-full group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(245,158,11,0.5)] mt-1"></div>
                        <div class="w-0.5 h-full bg-blue-800 mt-2"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-slate-100 flex-grow group-hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-950 mb-1 flex items-center gap-2"><span>🧘‍♂️</span> Wake Up & Yoga</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs md:text-sm leading-relaxed">Mandatory physical activity and Yoga sessions to build stamina, flexibility, and absolute mental focus.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4 group">
                    <div class="md:w-28 shrink-0 text-left md:text-right pt-2">
                        <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-white block leading-none">08:00 AM</span>
                        <span class="text-blue-400 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wide">School</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden md:flex flex-col items-center">
                        <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-blue-500 rounded-full group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(59,130,246,0.5)] mt-1"></div>
                        <div class="w-0.5 h-full bg-blue-800 mt-2"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-slate-100 flex-grow group-hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-950 mb-1 flex items-center gap-2"><span>🏫</span> Regular Classes</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs md:text-sm leading-relaxed">Students attend regular classes, deeply engaging with our expert faculty across all subjects.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4 group">
                    <div class="md:w-28 shrink-0 text-left md:text-right pt-2">
                        <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-white block leading-none">02:30 PM</span>
                        <span class="text-orange-400 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wide">Afternoon</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden md:flex flex-col items-center">
                        <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-orange-500 rounded-full group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(249,115,22,0.5)] mt-1"></div>
                        <div class="w-0.5 h-full bg-blue-800 mt-2"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-slate-100 flex-grow group-hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-950 mb-1 flex items-center gap-2"><span>👨‍🏫</span> Remedial classes</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs md:text-sm leading-relaxed">Dedicated afternoon session for completing homework and clearing daily school doubts under expert guidance.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4 group">
                    <div class="md:w-28 shrink-0 text-left md:text-right pt-2">
                        <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-white block leading-none">04:30 PM</span>
                        <span class="text-green-400 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wide">Evening</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden md:flex flex-col items-center">
                        <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-green-500 rounded-full group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(34,197,94,0.5)] mt-1"></div>
                        <div class="w-0.5 h-full bg-blue-800 mt-2"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-slate-100 flex-grow group-hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-950 mb-1 flex items-center gap-2"><span>⚽</span> Sports & Mind Games</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs md:text-sm leading-relaxed">Students engage in physical sports or indoor mind games (Chess, Carrom) to relieve stress.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-6 group">
                    <div class="md:w-28 shrink-0 text-left md:text-right pt-2">
                        <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-white block leading-none">06:30 PM</span>
                        <span class="text-purple-400 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wide">Night</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden md:flex flex-col items-center">
                        <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-purple-500 rounded-full group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(168,85,247,0.5)] mt-1"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-slate-100 flex-grow group-hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-950 mb-1 flex items-center gap-2"><span>📚</span> Supervised study & Dinner</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs md:text-sm leading-relaxed">Strict supervised study hours for homework, followed by dinner before bedtime.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="details" class="relative z-40 -mt-8 md:-mt-12 pt-16 pb-20 md:pt-24 md:pb-32 bg-white rounded-t-[2.5rem] md:rounded-t-[4rem] shadow-[0_-15px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
            
            <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
                <span class="text-amber-600 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-2 block">Why Parents Trust Us</span>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-black text-blue-950 mb-6">Every Detail. Carefully Managed.</h2>
                <div class="w-24 h-1.5 bg-amber-500 mx-auto rounded-full mb-8"></div>
                <p class="text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    We leave nothing to chance. From security protocols to the exact nutritional value of our meals, explore the unmatched facilities of the LKEA Hostel.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3 md:gap-8 lg:gap-10">
                
                <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-4 md:p-8 border border-slate-200 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-2xl hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col h-full group relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-[8px] md:text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-2 md:px-4 py-0.5 md:py-1 rounded-bl-lg md:rounded-bl-xl">Academics</div>
                    
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-blue-950 text-white rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl md:text-3xl mb-3 md:mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-transform shadow-lg shrink-0">👨‍🏫</div>
                    
                    <h3 class="text-[13px] md:text-2xl font-black text-blue-950 mb-2 md:mb-4 leading-tight">Supervised Evening Study</h3>
                    <div class="w-8 md:w-12 h-1 bg-amber-400 mb-3 md:mb-5 rounded-full"></div>
                    
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-[10px] md:text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4 md:mb-8 flex-grow">
                        Academics don't stop after school hours. Our residential teachers personally guide students every evening. This rigorous prep is the secret behind our high success rate in competitive exams like Navodaya vidyalaya.
                    </p>
                    
                    <ul class="space-y-1.5 md:space-y-3 border-t border-slate-200 pt-3 md:pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-[8px] md:text-xs">✔</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-sm text-blue-950 font-bold leading-tight">daily homework completion checking.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-[8px] md:text-xs">✔</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-sm text-blue-950 font-bold leading-tight">Individual doubt-clearing attention.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-[8px] md:text-xs">✔</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-sm text-blue-950 font-bold leading-tight">Specialized test prep for weaker subjects.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-4 md:p-8 border border-slate-200 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-2xl hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col h-full group relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 text-[8px] md:text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-2 md:px-4 py-0.5 md:py-1 rounded-bl-lg md:rounded-bl-xl">Nutrition</div>
                    
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-blue-950 text-white rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl md:text-3xl mb-3 md:mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:-rotate-3 transition-transform shadow-lg shrink-0">🍛</div>
                    
                    <h3 class="text-[13px] md:text-2xl font-black text-blue-950 mb-2 md:mb-4 leading-tight">Ghar Jaisa Khana</h3>
                    <div class="w-8 md:w-12 h-1 bg-amber-400 mb-3 md:mb-5 rounded-full"></div>
                    
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-[10px] md:text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4 md:mb-8 flex-grow">
                        We understand children miss home. Our dedicated kitchen provides pure vegetarian, hygienic, and highly nutritious meals cooked with utmost care to ensure child stays healthy and energetic
                    </p>
                    
                    <ul class="space-y-1.5 md:space-y-3 border-t border-slate-200 pt-3 md:pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-[8px] md:text-xs">✔</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-sm text-blue-950 font-bold leading-tight">Strictly pure vegetarian & hygienic kitchen.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-[8px] md:text-xs">✔</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-sm text-blue-950 font-bold leading-tight">Menu planned for growing children's nutrition.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-[8px] md:text-xs">✔</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-sm text-blue-950 font-bold leading-tight">RO filtered safe drinking water available 24/7.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-4 md:p-8 border border-slate-200 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-2xl hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col h-full group relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-red-100 text-red-800 text-[8px] md:text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-2 md:px-4 py-0.5 md:py-1 rounded-bl-lg md:rounded-bl-xl">Safety</div>
                    
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-blue-950 text-white rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl md:text-3xl mb-3 md:mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-transform shadow-lg shrink-0">📹</div>
                    
                    <h3 class="text-[13px] md:text-2xl font-black text-blue-950 mb-2 md:mb-4 leading-tight">Impenetrable Security</h3>
                    <div class="w-8 md:w-12 h-1 bg-amber-400 mb-3 md:mb-5 rounded-full"></div>
                    
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-[10px] md:text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4 md:mb-8 flex-grow">
                        Child's safety is our highest priority. The campus is a highly secure zone with strict entry/exit protocols, ensuring no unauthorized access is ever permitted.
                    </p>
                    
                    <ul class="space-y-1.5 md:space-y-3 border-t border-slate-200 pt-3 md:pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-[8px] md:text-xs">✔</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-sm text-blue-950 font-bold leading-tight">Comprehensive 24×7 CCTV camera surveillance.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-[8px] md:text-xs">✔</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-sm text-blue-950 font-bold leading-tight">Highly trained on-site residential Wardens.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-[8px] md:text-xs">✔</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-sm text-blue-950 font-bold leading-tight">Zero-tolerance policy for indiscipline.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-4 md:p-8 border border-slate-200 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-2xl hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col h-full group relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 text-[8px] md:text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-2 md:px-4 py-0.5 md:py-1 rounded-bl-lg md:rounded-bl-xl">Wellness</div>
                    
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-blue-950 text-white rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl md:text-3xl mb-3 md:mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:-rotate-3 transition-transform shadow-lg shrink-0">🧘‍♂️</div>
                    
                    <h3 class="text-[13px] md:text-2xl font-black text-blue-950 mb-2 md:mb-4 leading-tight">Yoga & Mental Sharpness</h3>
                    <div class="w-8 md:w-12 h-1 bg-amber-400 mb-3 md:mb-5 rounded-full"></div>
                    
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-[10px] md:text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4 md:mb-8 flex-grow">
                        A healthy mind resides in a healthy body. We enforce a strict but enjoyable routine to build physical stamina and mental focus, crucial for young, developing minds.
                    </p>
                    
                    <ul class="space-y-1.5 md:space-y-3 border-t border-slate-200 pt-3 md:pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-[8px] md:text-xs">✔</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-sm text-blue-950 font-bold leading-tight">Compulsory morning Yoga & meditation.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-[8px] md:text-xs">✔</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-sm text-blue-950 font-bold leading-tight">Structured indoor mind games (Chess, Carrom).</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-1.5 md:gap-3">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-[8px] md:text-xs">✔</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-sm text-blue-950 font-bold leading-tight">Dedicated time for outdoor physical sports.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
